divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving n on I-65 in Indiana mile marker 189 right before rainstorm off to east maybe 500-700 feet & it was traveling slow & maybe 100-200 feet in air over an open field, I was on cell & 17 yr old daughter goes "Mom, what is that? is that a UFO? oh my God!", well I almost wrecked my car but I described to my husband on phone- round with lights flashing around it & lights were like the color of halogen headlights, kind of blueish, we couldn't stop because of traffic, but it was moving slow & didn't jet off in a strange manner or anything. I told daughter to take a picture w digital camera but it didn't look like anything that would be believeable so she deleted it. Very curious if anyone else saw anything.
Summary: round w lights flashing around it in sequence
